Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier 而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.23,0:00:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.47,0:00:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.18,0:00:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.58,0:00:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.42,0:00:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.16,0:00:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.67,0:00:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.64,0:00:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.24,0:00:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.28,0:01:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.78,0:01:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.29,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.90,0:01:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.50,0:01:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C. 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.15,0:01:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,查到那傢伙的底細了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.85,0:01:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收穫不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.99,0:01:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安全防護比預計還要嚴密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.79,0:01:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為情報廳是由戰前就存在的數個情報組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.36,0:01:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及舊防衛局合併而成的最新行政組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.93,0:01:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，合田所屬的戰略影響調查會議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.00,0:01:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在國內外情報收集、分析以及自衛軍的行動等方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.77,0:02:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我倒是找到許多非法操作情報的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.68,0:02:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鈽的這件案子也是其中之一吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.22,0:02:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙的經歷呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.89,0:02:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從防衛局被挖角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.35,0:02:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一口氣爬到現在的位子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.39,0:02:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是當時的記錄並不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.03,0:02:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直就是吊車尾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.76,0:02:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是一個無法摸清底細的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.57,0:02:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田在防衛局時代的長相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.47,0:02:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是在某次事故中受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.77,0:02:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他到現在還是保留了當時的傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.91,0:02:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如現在那樣令人印象深刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.78,0:02:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.98,0:02:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時停止挖他的底細
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.08,0:02:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去接受課長的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.88,0:02:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熬夜之後馬上就參加午餐會議啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.94,0:03:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#08 素食的晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.41,0:03:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急集合各位不為別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.48,0:03:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是要告訴各位面對近來接連發生的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該如何應對的方針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.62,0:03:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前我想狠狠揍那個混蛋一頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.36,0:03:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內廳的行為很明顯是對我們施壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受過兩次氣後我可不想保持沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也跟你們一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.57,0:03:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘴上雖這麼說，可是你最近好像常常去總理那邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.61,0:03:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想在我們脖子上套韁繩的不就是首相本人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.48,0:03:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她雖然是為了將社會的目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.78,0:03:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從前政權賄賂案件移開所推出來的花瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.89,0:03:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，她只可能成為朋友不會變成敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.13,0:04:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想少校這邊也獨自進行過調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.63,0:04:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在內閣情報廳之內對陸自直升機失控事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.77,0:04:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及前幾天的鈽運送事件很明顯有人意圖操作情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.14,0:04:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前雖然不確定內廳對這些事件有什麼樣的企圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.88,0:04:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，我認為數次對我們施壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.12,0:04:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是政府內部想隱瞞某些事情的行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.29,0:04:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個別的11人事件也是一樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.32,0:04:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.26,0:04:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以面對首相暗殺未遂這種重大恐怖活動時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才會把立場最接近的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.43,0:04:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,排除在調查活動之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.54,0:04:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使總理是紙老虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果對抗政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們還是等於反咬主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使如此還是要繼續嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是在等這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.58,0:04:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我來說明作戰計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏提出來的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.56,0:05:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都是自稱個別的11人的個別犯罪集團所犯的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.37,0:05:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,JNN電視台捐款非法挪用事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.54,0:05:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民援助團體爆炸事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.61,0:05:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐嚇對難民無償提供義體的NP0團體的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.61,0:05:23.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,NPO：Non-Profit Organization 非營利性服務機構
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.05,0:05:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地下義體醫生溺死事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.55,0:05:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,網路銀行總經理被火車輾死事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.36,0:05:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,民政黨議員刺殺事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.33,0:05:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人氣電子腦饒舌歌手「傳說」槍殺事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.76,0:05:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南陽報社恐嚇事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.80,0:05:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.24,0:05:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茅葺總理暗殺未遂事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這九個事件當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.61,0:05:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以往認為只有首相暗殺事件才有目擊到嫌犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.31,0:06:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，我發現另一個事件也有目擊到可能是嫌疑犯的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.29,0:06:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我第一次聽到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.82,0:06:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察廳不是一直拒絕提供情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.13,0:06:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟笑面男事件的時候不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.16,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們也本著相當的覺悟進行調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.96,0:06:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事實上那本來就是不必要的障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.70,0:06:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是來自警方而是事件當事人自己取得的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南陽的記者嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.78,0:06:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.74,0:06:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以往南陽報社因為對難民政策採取批判的態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.08,0:06:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辦公大樓三度遭到個別的11人開槍射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.85,0:06:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而在所有事件發生的時候防盜攝影機上每次都有拍到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.99,0:06:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.43,0:06:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他名叫川島翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大約一個月前開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.13,0:06:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以台灣素食廚師的身份在南陽報社附近的餐廳工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.90,0:06:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還發現他有擔任自衛官的經歷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.47,0:06:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個情報從哪裏來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.87,0:07:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發出他的臉部骨骼資料後得到軍方情報部的協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.75,0:07:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到最後我們的親戚關係還是軍方比警方親近啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我們怎麼處置這傢伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.89,0:07:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先抓住這個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.66,0:07:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,調查他的思想和背景關係中隱藏的意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.33,0:07:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前雖然不能確定內廳和個別的11人有何關聯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.73,0:07:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但只要瞭解他們藉由什麼媒介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.00,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓Stand Alone的恐怖份子團體出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.97,0:07:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以看穿他們的意圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.54,0:07:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特與托古薩、齋藤、帕茲去抓川島翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.41,0:07:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川與波瑪除了繼續挖掘合田的內幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.18,0:07:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同時還要檢索調查首相暗殺未遂的實行犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.82,0:07:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.94,0:08:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣總算變得比較像我們課了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.81,0:08:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是搞不太懂這兩個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個別的11人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是其它七個事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然「解放難民」這句口號相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是怎樣都找不到一致性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.32,0:08:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了犯罪聲明上印的標誌以外也沒有任何共通點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.80,0:08:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這跟笑面男事件性質相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，這些模仿者的原始版本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.07,0:08:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該就是死守中國大使館的那群人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.37,0:08:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟是他們最早自稱個別的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.64,0:08:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是除了他們之外反而沒有人這麼稱呼自己啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.91,0:08:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就連我們也是在調查那個標誌的過程中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.95,0:08:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到某位思想家的評論才知道該怎麼念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在Stand Alone型的事件當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.26,0:09:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形成動機的媒介者不必然就是原版，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.93,0:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，我還是覺得使用這個標誌的那群人比較有原創性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.34,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好難吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.47,0:09:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼啊?這不是義體人用食品嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.31,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃不死人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,材料是90%的麵筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.38,0:09:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及用氨基酸為基礎材料的少量微機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.22,0:09:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，狀況如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.85,0:09:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有收穫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經四天以上沒回公寓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.36,0:09:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去報社那邊監視看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.79,0:09:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們來得太晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.66,0:09:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是難得的情報 失去新鮮度後也沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.04,0:09:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要照這樣繼續監視下去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.67,0:09:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然以抓到他本人為最優先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了重視可能性之外別無他法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.84,0:09:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他應該還繼續在恐嚇南陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.88,0:09:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且到昨天為止還有到店裏上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.85,0:09:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣做不怎麼主動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.92,0:10:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了彌補數量不足我送援軍過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.12,0:10:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三台塔奇克馬並不能提高監視的效率啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.83,0:10:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼說嘛，托古薩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們能在維持個體差異的狀況下進行同步化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.47,0:10:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還追加了代理機能喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.24,0:10:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來就像能做「幽體分離」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.68,0:10:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就可以身體留在現場 源源不斷地去擷取情報了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們把這個叫作「情報的宴會」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閒聊到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提高IR系統的檢索能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,IR系統：InformationRetrieval–System 包含N系統[汽車牌號自動讀取系統]在內的情報檢索系統的總稱\N也作為危險預防系統，是公安監視網的組成部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.26,0:10:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,積極逮捕川島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.92,0:10:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宴會!宴會!宴會!宴會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——開宴會羅!宴會!宴會!\N少校什麼時候裝了這種設備啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.07,0:10:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近我們的確人手不足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.31,0:10:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來以為假裝要換裝PKF型號的義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.41,0:10:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們一定會露出馬腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會已經不在國內了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.78,0:11:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我懷疑是內廳操作過情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.52,0:11:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在地方網路上找到有趣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.86,0:11:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田學生時代的畢業論文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.79,0:11:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在培養社會性的前提下電子腦應尊重個性還是協調性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.60,0:11:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從生產者的立場來談英雄論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.34,0:11:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內容出乎意料很令人感興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.97,0:11:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像標題也有提到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.21,0:11:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他指出現在的社會構造裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.78,0:11:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電子腦隨著「個體」的消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.38,0:11:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於無意識當中表現出追求協調性的傾向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應用這個原理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.65,0:11:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他認為可以將有意識地控制無意識大眾的領導人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.52,0:11:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創造成為社會系統的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.32,0:11:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像在解構笑面男事件的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.03,0:11:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過光看寫的日期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這篇文章完成的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.30,0:11:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比笑面男事件還要更早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.84,0:12:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來那傢伙又學了情報化學、情報倫理、應用情報論等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.54,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一度曾於民間企業就職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.98,0:12:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,民間?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.61,0:12:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在在義體技術和微機械製造上眾所皆知的超級跨國企業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波賽頓工業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是當時的大日本技研
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.10,0:12:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用超速公路前往博多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.20,0:12:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.67,0:12:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉我挪不出太多時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幾點會到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟約定的時間一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那到上次那家店如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.42,0:12:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不便在太公開的場合跟你見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.59,0:12:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我先過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.67,0:13:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.87,0:13:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近都不能好好回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.11,0:13:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道那是什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.11,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是鰻魚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.38,0:13:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點小事我還是知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.32,0:13:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是用麵筋和香菇當材料所做出來的假鰻魚料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,台灣素食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.19,0:13:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是所謂的「素菜」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.09,0:13:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自古以來乃一部分僧侶自己研發出來的特殊料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,類似精進料理嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精進料理：起源於平安時代的日本素食\N包含了禪宗的精進精神之意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.53,0:13:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.87,0:13:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，跟日本精進料理不同的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.34,0:13:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是不直接調理食材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.67,0:13:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是對豆類和香菇加工重現出肉或魚的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.88,0:13:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你吃剩的三明治是同樣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.92,0:13:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.39,0:13:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼台灣的和尚會想出這麼麻煩的料理法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果一開始就不知道肉的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不就沒有這種必要了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話是這麼說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.00,0:14:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論是誰在進佛門之前都是可以隨便吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.57,0:14:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管修行有多深還是無法消除當時的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.81,0:14:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，你還真是清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.18,0:14:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道老大也開始懷念起真正的味道了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.12,0:14:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是義體人腦部對食慾還是會有需求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.72,0:14:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才會製造出當成娛樂使用的義體人食品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.99,0:14:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了想起過去的記憶「味道」扮演再生裝置的角色嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.90,0:14:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,川島那傢伙是在哪裏學到這種料理的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.60,0:14:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多半是駐留台灣的時候學的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.97,0:14:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們幾個好好監視喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.58,0:14:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.85,0:14:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然今晚的主題是難民問題和恐怖主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.02,0:15:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想先把這段時間的事情經過再整理一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.89,0:15:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去政策目標的政府之怠慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.49,0:15:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,促使個別主義者抬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.86,0:15:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了在維新中找出答案的激進因子登上舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.37,0:15:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以這麼解釋嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.57,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是因為現在的政權太軟弱才出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的政權上台之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.94,0:15:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國防出身的議員就在考慮簽定新美日安保條約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.84,0:15:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們說現在動手可以從美國手中搶到主導權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.55,0:15:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個別主義其實早跟這股潮流同時存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.55,0:15:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓個別主義者激進起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.25,0:15:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如說是浪費稅金的三百萬難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.19,0:15:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說我們國家已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多該處理那些傢伙的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.53,0:15:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此，一開始就不要接收不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說出這句話就無法繼續討論了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.47,0:15:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來的難民處理法強迫國民增加多少稅金呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.51,0:16:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且那些稅金以難民處理當藉口都消失在黑暗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——有誰在嗎? ——這種只會引發犯罪的處置法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.02,0:16:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我把現在33頻道播的政論節目的錄影光碟拿過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——我知道了 ——執政黨不知為何還不廢除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——當然還要繼續錄影喔 ——那也無可奈何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.79,0:16:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果很快就去刺激難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.03,0:16:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們更是不會善罷甘休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,俗稱的自爆恐怖攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.50,0:16:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是對自己的未來不抱任何希望之時的最終手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.11,0:16:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此有必要促使他們自發性的走向自立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.81,0:16:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給他們名為解放的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.35,0:16:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡說些什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.28,0:16:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算給難民自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.35,0:16:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們也不可能自己解決自己的問題不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.01,0:17:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.78,0:17:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去比對那台車的車牌號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然已經針對數個恐怖活動討論過整體案情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.95,0:17:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們提出具體的問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——是那時候的 ——土橋先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.42,0:17:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個警察廳一心想隱瞞的恐怖活動是什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.19,0:17:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事件本身我想大家也都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.83,0:17:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中國大使館佔領事件以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.37,0:17:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您應該知道發生了八件左右的恐怖攻擊事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指電子腦音樂家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.54,0:17:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有對難民主張和睦政策的議員被刺殺的事情嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.34,0:17:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這些事件當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.31,0:17:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有個警察廳完全未對媒體公佈的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.82,0:17:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要裝模作樣了，快點說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.49,0:17:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看過這個標誌嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.02,0:17:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基本上是登記在連鎖店名下的普通車輛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.03,0:17:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送來當作犯罪聲明的信件上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.20,0:18:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通通都印有這個標誌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.37,0:18:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——這傢伙為什麼知道這個? ——從來沒聽過這種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——怎麼樣？ ——我也沒聽過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.10,0:18:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——監視都交給塔奇克馬啦? ——情報來自哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.61,0:18:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——不...不是 ——那是企業機密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——拿去 ——那就沒有說服力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——不是吃東西的時候了 ——那要是知道這個標誌的念法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——怎麼啦?這可是真的喔 ——你們也多少會吃驚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.02,0:18:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是那個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.39,0:18:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——這傢伙是我以前見過的記者之— ——這個標誌讀作個別的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.52,0:18:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——他竟然知道事件的機密情報 ——源自半世紀前某本評論集的篇名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.23,0:18:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用這個名稱發動事件的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.70,0:18:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在解放難民的動機之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.73,0:18:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現沒有橫向聯繫的個別集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——這傢伙在說什麼啊 ——以自衛軍直升機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.04,0:18:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在難民街上空盤旋為契機 個別主義者開始現身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們這些行動者的動機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.61,0:18:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—— 竟然有這種感染案例啊 ——是真心想解放難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.68,0:18:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.22,0:18:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,——因為不能過度降低警察的品格 ——抱歉打斷各位討論，我們進廣告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想他是很好的點火角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.79,0:19:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此外，南陽事件和首相暗殺事件的感染者呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.03,0:19:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.83,0:19:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於南陽的感染者已經對公安1課操縱完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.17,0:19:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想很快就能清除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.44,0:19:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於嘗試暗殺首相的感染者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.24,0:19:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜想可能是因為PKF去半島的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名叫久世英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.04,0:19:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是透過感染因子反推回去所得到的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.08,0:19:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想應該沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.48,0:19:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.95,0:19:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於合田那個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.29,0:19:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算問防衛局時代的同僚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.66,0:19:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也幾乎沒有人記得他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.93,0:19:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也只記得他很沒有存在感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.57,0:19:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，我找到了錄用時的精神分析測驗記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.74,0:19:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然內向，卻有很強的自我意識和自我炫耀欲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.58,0:19:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反過來說也有利用他人來表現自己的傾向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.02,0:20:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟現在的他感覺上多少有點不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?不吃嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,味道跟以前一樣沒變喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟以前一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.40,0:20:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有你上次問的那個叫作川島的自衛官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.24,0:20:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公安1課也向我們詢問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.14,0:20:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是一個叫王崇廉的殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.81,0:20:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偷了川島的臉躲在中華街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.15,0:20:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以來跟我們要臉的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.05,0:20:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事為什麼不早說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.98,0:20:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為你已經跟他們聯絡過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.99,0:20:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.39,0:20:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1課會調查跟南陽不同的案子實在很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.29,0:20:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點通知巴特他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.26,0:20:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經在通知了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.06,0:20:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說到王崇廉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.53,0:20:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是台灣出身的國際恐怖份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.60,0:20:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面雖然下達了暗殺命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是沒接到他變臉的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.94,0:20:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我們被陷害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.57,0:20:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是1課被陷害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.84,0:20:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是哪一種這個時間點實在很微妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.41,0:20:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.25,0:21:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了以防萬一控制住剛剛那輛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.18,0:21:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.15,0:21:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標在店後面出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.95,0:21:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.40,0:21:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然這個國家給難民住太奢侈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.27,0:21:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也還沒富裕到可以收容難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.44,0:21:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是王崇廉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.28,0:21:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.85,0:21:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壓住它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.95,0:21:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Roger
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.39,0:21:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把槍放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.26,0:21:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,川島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.80,0:21:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐下別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.34,0:22:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.01,0:22:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巷子太窄沒辦法幫他擋子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.25,0:22:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是1課的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.05,0:22:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.35,0:22:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.25,0:22:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仔細看看這傢伙的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.09,0:22:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他沒有連臉都義體化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.22,0:22:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說他不是王崇廉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.76,0:22:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.33,0:22:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1課得到了確實的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.87,0:22:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是素子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.77,0:22:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也被設計了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.70,0:22:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我們一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.61,0:23:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.32,0:23:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.79,0:23:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.76,0:23:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的美麗事物
